A simple webapp that uses apache javaflow continuations to handle application flow.

Environment
-----------
I built and run the application using:

apache-maven-2.2.1
oracle java jdk1.7.0_02
apache-tomcat-7.0.28

Build webapp
------------
From a shell cd to the pom.xml directory and run the following

mvn clean package

Then copy target/javaflow.web.war under webapp folder of tomcat.

Run
---
Start tomcat, open a browser and type the following url to test the application:

http://localhost:8080/javaflow.web/FlowServlet
